, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":60,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBUQ040EGAYiEwjwv8Tlt-uTAxX1RvIAHYiVIH9I3K28i_CFudy4AcoBBI0jwm8=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa1Q4cmo4M1UxRGhrZEpSMXdxOWtxMzBXMncxZ3xBQ3Jtc0ttZVduRHFjWnZqOHJ2bW0tUHVNdVl1OW1uakZzQWRaOERXcDNNNV9hUVluQVhIckx6VkQ2QjdBWlI1QjIwRHdWdGtZbHBUOGptX3hsZWZUVnhhSjIzOHNzOVBTMFJYSTMyZkZmTUd6eU9wOWctTHc3aw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=uLjkLwFvFtw","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa1Q4cmo4M1UxRGhrZEpSMXdxOWtxMzBXMncxZ3xBQ3Jtc0ttZVduRHFjWnZqOHJ2bW0tUHVNdVl1OW1uakZzQWRaOERXcDNNNV9hUVluQVhIckx6VkQ2QjdBWlI1QjIwRHdWdGtZbHBUOGptX3hsZWZUVnhhSjIzOHNzOVBTMFJYSTMyZkZmTUd6eU9wOWctTHc3aw\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=uLjkLwFvFtw","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":172,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBUQ040EGAYiEwjwv8Tlt-uTAxX1RvIAHYiVIH9I3K28i_CFudy4AcoBBI0jwm8=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa2x1bUNKdG9aZUZjSXJpYmtkQ2xpMTlKWmlaUXxBQ3Jtc0tuODJlWUhNNjZWcDgzSlloM3ZMUjQ2RlNUa0trcUhibDBfVzN5UUZSOVFwWmlqcEhNT3l4RjZXRGhvOGxaS2ZtLWdRQVdaSW8tTElPNHRLVm1rbWNFaU5vWWR5NlQ4UnY5blpyMkk1S2JiajZvdTR5SQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paypal.com%2Fcgi-bin%2Fwebscr%3Fcmd%3D_s-xclick%26hosted_button_id%3D64QMB